summary:
PUTinCoin – MOBILE WALLET RELEASED!!! - PUTinCoin has released its mobile wallet, providing users with a convenient way to manage their coins.

 Fan creates outstanding video about PUTinCoin - A fan has created an exceptional video showcasing the features and benefits of PUTinCoin.

 XEGGEX lists PUTinCoin - PUTinCoin has been listed on the XEGGEX exchange, allowing users to trade the coin.

 PUTinCoin – NODE WALLETS UPDATED!!! - PUTinCoin has released an update for its node wallets, improving the functionality and security.

 MIDJOURNEYS PUTiNZ NFT collection + PUTinCoin airdrop + VIDEO!! - MIDJOURNEYS has launched the PUTiNZ NFT collection and is conducting a PUTinCoin airdrop. A video showcasing the collection and airdrop has also been released.
